  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had met him in his-- in his-- where he lived, where he was teaching.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wouldn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I presume so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That is on the-- on [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Villenska ?] Street, yeah, called [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Villenska ?] Street.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The main rabbi, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was the main rabbi.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We came and asked him, Rabbi, help us, Jewish students to get-- to get a cadaver.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, please, no, you must understand-- he was very human-- you must understand me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Said, I would like to help you as much as possible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this is a Jewish law that if a Jew died, within 24 hours, he has to be interred, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and I cannot help you.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We came in-- oh, three-- three, from the 20-something Jew-- Jews, we-- I was the leading.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kapinski ?] was with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and-- I forgot-- from a very famous Jewish-- Jewish-- from a Jewish family very famous in Vilna, she was the third one.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- maybe I recall her name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, it is-- it is just-- [INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, after we finished our conversation, we said, rabbi, thank you very much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He turned to us [INAUDIBLE] stretched the hand, shake-- shook hands with me, shook hands with doctor-- doctor-- with-- at that time, [?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Tom ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kapinski, ?] and they-- and the other--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She stretches her hand, and he makes 180 degree turn at the side.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kapinski, ?] who knew more about religion, put her hand down, and we left, and he told her that a rabbi will never give a hand to a woman.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He didn't give us any suggestions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I made many suggestions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nevertheless, maybe indirect, nevertheless, in Jewish hospital, one died.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We can-- we-- we-- we got this-- this body, and we had a body to-- but we didn't have-- so we needed at least, four or five bodies, you know, but it is with only one body, so 20 some, one would section the arms, the other with the-- the-- the legs, and the other the bowels, and the other--",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Finished, you brought back, you know, brought back to a burial.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To a Jewish burial.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was-- I was accepted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was not accepted-- I was called to go for one year to the Polish army, after I graduated from medical school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1933.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I was, you know, [INAUDIBLE] pleased.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would-- I like to go straight, you know, in-- into my profession.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But if I had to go for one year to the army, I went to the army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was in-- in-- in-- in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a special medical-- military medical school for professional doctor-- for professional military doctors, and-- and we were all a part of this for only [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when we were called to duty.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we went--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was happier in the school, medical school, this military medical school, where we-- we had a-- from one side, simple medical-- simple military education.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- and the-- besides we had lectures on military medicine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the students were already-- we were-- Jews were already only around 10 in 120.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Something-- we have to stop?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
